Jean Carmen https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean_Carmen 0 For the similarly named B-movie actress and pinup girl (1930-2007), see Jeanne CarmenJean Carmen (April 7, 1913 – August 26, 1993), was an American film, stage, and radio actress of the 1930s. She also went by the stage name Julia Thayer.
